				\begin{document}$$\Delta W=\frac{{G}_{f}-{G}_{i}}{{G}_{i}}\times 100\%$$\end{document}

Figure 4d depicts the synaptic weight change as a function of the spike time interval Δt. The data show an STDP-like behavior, while a Gaussian function of the following form was used to fit the data:ΔW=A·exp-Δt22τ2+W0\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
